<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="no">
<head>
	<title>SiO Dagens middag</title>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=0, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/forkandknife.png" />
	<!-- jquery mobile -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="jquery.mobile-1.3.1.css" />
	<script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.min.js"></script>
	<script src="http://code.jquery.com/mobile/1.3.2/jquery.mobile-1.3.2.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
	function loadDetails(cantinaId){
		$.mobile.changePage("/cantina/"+cantinaId);
	}
	</script>
	<style type="text/css">
		.ui-header .ui-title {
		    margin-right: 10%;
		    margin-left: 10%;
		}
	</style>
	<!--Add to homescreen -->
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="add2home.css">
	<script type="application/javascript" src="add2home.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div data-role="page" id="cantinas">
	<header data-role="header">
		<h1>SiO - Dagens middag</h1>
	</header>
	<article data-role="content">
		<ul data-role="listview">
			<% for @cantina in allCantinas %>
			<li>
				<a onClick="loadDetails(<%= @cantina.id %>)">
					<h1><%= @cantina.name %></h1>
				</a>
			</li>
  			<% end %>
		</ul>
	</article>
	<footer data-role="footer" data-position="fixed">
		<nav data-role="navbar">
			<ul>
				<li><a href="#cantinas" data-icon="home">Hjem</a></li>
				<li><a href="#info" data-icon="info">Info</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</footer>
</div>
	
<div data-role="page" id="info">
	<header data-role="header">
		<h1>Info</h1>
	</header>
	<p>SiO Dagens middag er en app laget for å lettere finne dagens middag hos Studensamskipnaden i Oslo sine kantiner. </p>
	<p><strong>SiO har ingen tilknytning til utviklinga av appen.</strong></p>
	<p>Appen fungerer ved at den besøker <a href="http://sio.no">sio.no</a> og henter informasjon om dagens middag og gjør den mer lesbar for mobile enheter.</p>
	<p>Utvikler av appen er meg: Ole Christian Langfjæran</p>
	<p>Twitter: <a href="https://twitter.com/judoole">@judoole</a></p>
	<p>Kildekode: <a href="https://github.com/judoole/SiOApp">github.com/judoole/SiOApp</a></p>
	<footer data-role="footer" data-position="fixed">
		<nav data-role="navbar">
			<ul>
				<li><a href="#cantinas" data-icon="home">Hjem</a></li>
				<li><a href="#info" data-icon="info">Info</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>
	</footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>